	<h2>SQL command</h2>
	<p>The SQL command starts a REPL for running or piping SurrealQL queries to a local or remote SurrealDB database server.</p>
	<blockquote yellow text="Before you start">Make sure you’ve <Link @link="docs.start.installation">installed SurrealDB</Link> — it should only take a second!</blockquote>
</Layout::Text>

